{"TopicId":152377,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Crash flying over northpole","CreatedByName":"bestimmaa","CreatedById":171760,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-21T19:26:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"bestimmaa","CreatedById":171760,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-21T19:26:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter 150 hours I encountered my first KSP crash while flying my tiny jet plane over north pole at ~10km. I was able reproduce this issue when loading a save game and do the 40-50 min flight there again. Time acceleration was at 4x most of the time before or during the flight over the pole. Over at the support section for consoles\u00A0someone\u00A0reported the same issue on PS4.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-21T19:31:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/83213-stock-support-bug-reporting-guide/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bestimmaa","CreatedById":171760,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-21T19:40:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter posting a few minutes ago and starting up KSP it crashed again. Right after take off. MEH\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3 Crash logs \u003Ca href=\u0022https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B3DtBoU7EzqTbTBGX1I3SGRPNzA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eattached \u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-21T19:44:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks I\u0027ll take a look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt looks like the highlighter bug, if you toggle the aero overlay on and off the next time you highlight your craft the game crashes, this bug doesn\u0027t exist on the consoles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe workaround is to disable the highlighter in flight from the settings screen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope this helps!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bestimmaa","CreatedById":171760,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T18:14:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for taking a look and providing me with this workaround\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was indeed trying to take a Steam screenshot with default key bindings - F12 which toggled the aero overlay. I also did this on my third attempt near \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E. (forgot to mention that\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E) - Neat skills. I\u0027m really surprised to get actual customer support enabling me to play the game again the next night. Keep it up \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-22T18:20:32Z\u0022 title=\u002211/22/2016 06:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 22, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by bestimmaa\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-23T12:04:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlad we could help \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}